# Git blame ignore revisions file
# This file contains commit hashes that should be ignored by git blame
# Useful for ignoring commits that only contain formatting changes

# Example: Add commit hashes for major formatting/style changes
# 1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678  # clang-format applied to entire codebase
# abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12  # Updated .clang-tidy rules across project

# How to use:
# git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
